                Hic situs est claro quondam qui nomine causas <lb n="2"/>oravit meruitque pater conscribtus <note>sic</note> haberi <lb n="3"/>nec longo post aevo dixit iura Viennae <lb n="4"/>inde iter Italiam magno cumulandus honore <lb n="5"/>ni luctu tristem linquens Eventius urbem <lb n="6"/>neu vitae merito sanctis sociandus obisset <lb n="7"/>bis vicenos vixit quarto recessit in anno <lb n="8"/>et geminam prolem sexu ex utroque reliquit <lb n="9"/>coniuge Faustina fisus quae victa dolore <lb n="10"/>transigeret <expan><abbr>vita</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> sed tenta pignore karo <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">pergere</supplied>t ut parvos <note>sic</note> defuncto debet amorem <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">atque</supplied> viro castam promisit ducere vitam <lb n="13"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">Ka</supplied>l</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d<am>d</am></abbr><ex>ominis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostris</ex></expan> Honorio VII et Theodosio II <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>ss</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
